OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775466313
OL,3,CArtemis II crew share 'extraordinary'
OL,4,Cviews after leaving Earth's orbit
OL,6,FThe Artemis II astronauts have shared
OL,7,Fthe "extraordinary things" they've
OL,8,Fwitnessed in space as they left
OL,9,FEarth's orbit on their mission to the
OL,10,Fmoon.
OL,12,FThe Orion spacecraft is now closer to
OL,13,Fthe moon than Earth, and the crew are
OL,14,Fon target to reach their destination
OL,15,Fby Monday, Nasa said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
