OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775466313
OL,3,CArtemis II crew share 'extraordinary'
OL,4,Cviews after leaving Earth's orbit
OL,6,FJeremy Hansen, the mission's only
OL,7,FCanadian crew member, described
OL,8,Ffeeling like the aircraft was "falling
OL,9,Fout of the sky back to Earth" when
OL,10,Fthey came back towards the planet for
OL,11,Fan injection manoeuvre.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
