FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775466313
OL,3,CArtemis II crew share 'extraordinary'
OL,4,Cviews after leaving Earth's orbit
OL,6,F"On our first day in space, we saw
OL,7,Fsome extraordinary things. The Earth
OL,8,Fup close. By the time we had a bit of
OL,9,Fa nap and got up, the Earth was just
OL,10,Fso far away again," Hansen said during
OL,11,Fa news conference from space.
OL,13,F"Then to come in for that transit or
OL,14,Finjection, we came all the way back to
OL,15,FEarth again.
OL,17,F"We were out there at 60,000km, we
OL,18,Fcame back to within 200km of the
OL,19,Fplanet, and it just felt like we were
OL,20,Ffalling out of the sky back to Earth."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
