FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775466313
OL,3,CArtemis II crew share 'extraordinary'
OL,4,Cviews after leaving Earth's orbit
OL,6,FHansen, who is on his first ever
OL,7,Fspaceflight, said it had felt like the
OL,8,FOrion was going to hit the Earth
OL,9,Fbecause of its proximity, describing
OL,10,Fthe experience as "really phenomenal".
OL,12,FFellow astronaut Victor Glover, who is
OL,13,FAmerican, also described seeing the
OL,14,F"Grand Canyon of the moon" known as
OL,15,Fthe Orientale Basin, which is not
OL,16,Fvisible from Earth.
OL,18,F"We were able to see the entire
OL,19,Fthing," he said, adding that the view
OL,20,Ffrom the Orion was "already special".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
