PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775466313
OL,3,CArtemis II crew share 'extraordinary'
OL,4,Cviews after leaving Earth's orbit
OL,6,FThe crew, who launched from Cape
OL,7,FCanaveral in Florida on Wednesday
OL,8,Fevening, are now over the halfway
OL,9,Fpoint to the moon.
OL,11,FThey are made up of mission specialist
OL,12,FHansen, pilot Glover, commander Reid
OL,13,FWiseman, and mission specialist
OL,14,FChristina Koch.
OL,16,FNasa released the astronaut's first
OL,17,Fphotos on Friday, with one showing a
OL,18,Fcurved slice of Earth in one of the
OL,19,Fcapsule's windows and another
OL,20,Fdepicting the entire globe topped by
OL,21,Fswirling white tendrils of clouds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
