PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775466313
OL,3,CArtemis II crew share 'extraordinary'
OL,4,Cviews after leaving Earth's orbit
OL,6,FThe crew have been "exercising,
OL,7,Fpracticing medical response
OL,8,Fprocedures, and testing the
OL,9,Fspacecraft's emergency communications
OL,10,Fsystem in deep space", the space
OL,11,Fagency said early Saturday morning.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
